|---|---|---|
| `--color-status-live` | #22c55e | Green dot for live/fallback states |
| `--color-status-reconnecting` | #f59e0b | Amber dot for reconnecting state |
| `--color-status-stale` | #ef4444 | Red dot for stale state, stale badge text |
| `--color-text-muted` | #606070 | Status text color (all states) |

