**Endpoint 2: `/coins/bitcoin/market_chart`** ‚Äî Historical hourly prices for chart

```
GET https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/coins/bitcoin/market_chart?vs_currency=usd&days=1
```

**Response format:**

```json
{
  "prices": [
    [1711843200000, 69702.31],
    [1711846800000, 69850.45],
    [1711850400000, 69623.18],
    [1711854000000, 69901.77],
