### CoinGecko API Rate Limits

CoinGecko free tier allows 30 requests per minute. With our 60-second polling interval making 2 requests per cycle (markets + chart), we use approximately 2 requests per minute ‚Äî well within the limit (NFR11).

If CoinGecko returns HTTP 429 (rate limit exceeded), the service treats it as a non-200 response: logs a warning, retains last store values, and tries again on the next poll cycle.

